    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable daily driver that won't break the bank? This vehicle is ready for its next chapter! It runs and drives well, offering a solid foundation for anyone looking for reliable transportation. While it shows some honest signs of use\u2014including some cosmetic wear and minor mechanical items that will need attention down the road\u2014it\u2019s a fantastic value for someone who prioritizes function and character. Come see the potential for yourself!",
