    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips or door dings, protected by a professional ceramic coating that makes the paint pop. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, and the original factory scent remains. Every button, switch, and electronic component functions perfectly, including the crisp infotainment system and climate control. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history and a documented life of climate-controlled storage. From the pristine engine bay to the spotless undercarriage, no detail has been overlooked. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
